== Fu Tung Estate == [[File:Fu Tung Estate.JPG|thumb|Fu Tung Estate]] Fu Tung Estate ({{zh|t=å¯æ±é¨}}) is located near [[Tung Chung Station]]. Built on the [[Land reclamation in Hong Kong|reclaimed land]] of [[North Lantau New Town]] Phase 1 project,<ref>[http://www.info.gov.hk/archive/napco/p-tung.html TUNG CHUNG NEW TOWN (Phase 1)]</ref> it is the first public housing estate in Tung Chung. It consists of 3 residential buildings completed in 1997.<ref>[http://www.emporis.com/en/wm/cx/?id=100783 Fu Tung Estate]</ref>
